review_blob: Sits quite nicely on the tongue. Malty flavor. Not overly strong alcohol presence. Very smooth start to a slightly bitter finish.
Very heavy texture. Thick flavor of dark chocolate/coffee. Itll sneak up on you. Two of them is the perfect amount.
beer_name: North Coast Old Rasputin Russian Imperial Stout

review_blob:
Caramel, roasty, smoke, woody
Doesnt have much of a head. Sits heavily on the tongue.
